Use JavaScript only.
Never use TypeScript.

Use Next.js App Router only.

Always prefer server components.

All routes must be dynamic and database-driven.

Use Prisma ORM for all database queries.

Never hardcode cities, states, or services.

Use reusable components only.

Use Tailwind CSS for styling.

All metadata must use generateMetadata.

All SEO pages must include:
- Spintext
- Nearby city internal links
- Dynamic metadata

Optimize Prisma queries.

Prefer createMany for bulk inserts.

Never expose environment variables.

Keep components modular and scalable.